<p>We camped at Buckenderra Holiday Village, situated at the bottom end of the lake. According to Steve, fishing has been exceptional in the last few years because new ground was flooded every year. Unfortunately, when we were there, the lake was low and weather conditions extremely hot (35 degrees celsius, 95 fahrenheit). Fishing was not good and no fish were caught the night before.</p>
<figure class="">
  &lt;a href=
    
      "/assets/images/2013/01/P1040398.jpg"
    
  <img src="/assets/images/2013/01/P1040398.jpg" alt="" />
  
