<p>&lt;/a&gt;</p>

<p>Although we were hoping to do better than a single fish in three solid days of fishing, we were rather lucky to catch any at all given the difficult conditions.¬†Lake Eucumbene is a beautiful and tranquil place, and I hope to return soon. It is particularly special to me as I caught my first trout on fly here under Steve‚Äôs guidance 20 years ago.</p>
